      <title>津巴布韦姆南加古瓦在小规模改组中任命新矿业部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/zimbabwe-leader-names-new-mines-minister-in-mini-reshuffle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦总统埃默森·姆南加古瓦重新任命温斯顿·奇坦多为这个南部非洲国家的矿业部长，他在去年选举前担任过这一职务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/zimbabwe-leader-names-new-mines-minister-in-mini-reshuffle</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 16:53:56 GMT</pubDate>
