    <item>
      <title>尽管有撤资法，拜登的竞选团队仍计划留在 TikTok</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/biden-s-campaign-plans-to-stay-on-tiktok-despite-divestment-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登的竞选团队表示，即使在他签署立法迫使其母公司北京字节跳动有限公司出售其股份，否则将面临美国应用商店的禁令后，他们仍将继续使用其在 TikTok 上的账户。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/biden-s-campaign-plans-to-stay-on-tiktok-despite-divestment-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 16:31:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯资产扣押法引发耶伦赞扬，美元担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/russia-asset-seizure-law-spurs-yellen-praise-angst-over-dollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国会周二通过授权总统乔·拜登扣押俄罗斯美元资产以援助乌克兰的新权力，加剧了有关外国对美国国债需求和使用美元的潜在后果的争论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/russia-asset-seizure-law-spurs-yellen-praise-angst-over-dollar</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 16:24:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙向科索沃库尔蒂施压，要求其在一体化方面取得进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/macron-pressures-kosovo-s-kurti-to-make-progress-on-integration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙敦促科索沃总理加大欧洲一体化的力度，告诉这位巴尔干领导人，他需要在向该国塞族少数民族提供一定程度的自治权方面取得进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/macron-pressures-kosovo-s-kurti-to-make-progress-on-integration</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 16:14:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>近一半的英国税务人员未能达到在办公室工作的目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/almost-half-of-uk-tax-collectors-miss-target-to-work-in-office</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据英国政府高级官员称，近一半的英国税务人员未能满足政府部门要求员工每周三天在办公室工作的要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/almost-half-of-uk-tax-collectors-miss-target-to-work-in-office</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 16:09:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉反对派领袖表示他愿意与马杜罗会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/venezuelan-opposition-leader-says-he-d-be-open-to-talks-with-maduro</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉反对派候选人埃德蒙多·冈萨雷斯表示，如果他赢得今年的选举，他将愿意与总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗进行会谈，以确保权力的顺利移交。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/venezuelan-opposition-leader-says-he-d-be-open-to-talks-with-maduro</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 16:07:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯国防部长绍伊古因关键盟友被捕而削弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/russian-defense-minister-shoigu-weakened-by-arrest-of-key-ally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，俄罗斯国防部长谢尔盖·绍伊古最亲密的盟友之一因涉嫌受贿被捕，削弱了他在总统弗拉基米尔·普京可能进行政府改组之前的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/russian-defense-minister-shoigu-weakened-by-arrest-of-key-ally</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 16:03:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙正在评估对将德拉吉任命为欧盟最高职位的计划的支持率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/macron-is-gauging-support-for-a-plan-to-install-draghi-in-the-top-eu-job</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五年前，法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙 (Emmanuel Macron) 帮助乌尔苏拉·冯德莱恩 (Ursula von der Leyen) 当选欧盟委员会主席，现在他正在与其他欧盟领导人进行谈判，寻找另一位候选人——比如马里奥·德拉吉——填补最高职位的空缺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/macron-is-gauging-support-for-a-plan-to-install-draghi-in-the-top-eu-job</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 13:37:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其的“正统”支点使里拉成为汇丰银行的最爱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/turkey-s-orthodox-pivot-makes-lira-a-favorite-for-hsbc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其回归更传统的货币政策方式正在提振投资者信心，为资本流入奠定基础，并支撑汇丰控股有限公司对该国资产的看涨立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/turkey-s-orthodox-pivot-makes-lira-a-favorite-for-hsbc</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 10:33:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
